t, and `src/agent_wrapper.py` orchestrates the trading bot via `src/trading_bot.py`. The user's instructions imply the need to integrate AppID handling, likely within `src/agent_wrapper.py` for spawning the trading bots with the `TARGET_APP_ID` environment variable. I'll check `src/trading_bot.py` next.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771162299528_138","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls src/trading_bot.py"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":9654,"output":1133,"cacheRead":5791,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10787,"cost":{"input":0.019308,"output":0.013596,"cacheRead":0.0011582,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0340622}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771162285707}}
